node.text: @busypeopleeat even with watermark???
@lowcarb_keto_fooddiary YES... I had someone do it to me and my account. It was sooooo blatant 😣

THANK YOU SO MUCH! ⁣
My IG friends and followers 💃💃💃
So many friends, even those who always remain silent rendered their help by alerting me and reporting that fellow. To you, it may be nothing but to me I am thankful. I love this IG community and i love you guys. Let's unite together and make it a pleasant platform to mingle, make friends and even share our joy with our posts. Remember ya, I will not ask for any personal details and even if I do, it will be phone exchange during our meetup which is more appropriate. If you are unsure, just drop me a PM and I will connect with you soonest. ⁣
⁣
⁣
💕 From today onwards, all my photos will come with my watermark. ⁣
